(1) Flatbush Ave., west side, north from 662, at extreme left. The frame home still stands. In 1890 were the property of C. King and T. Maynard.

April 1929.

(2) The same, a year earlier.

September 1928.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3) The same, not including buildings at extreme end.

July 1928.
